---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Creadores UGC | Pixel 360">
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 md:pt-40 md:pb-28 bg-primary overflow-hidden">
<div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-gutter grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center relative z-10">
<div class="space-y-6">
<h1 class="font-display-hero-mobile md:font-display-hero text-display-hero-mobile md:text-display-hero text-on-primary">
                CREADORES UGC
            </h1>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-primary/90 max-w-xl">
                Humaniza tu marca e impulsa tus ventas con contenido auténtico creado por usuarios reales. El "boca a boca" adaptado a la era digital.
            </p>
</div>
<div class="relative">
<img alt="UGC Concept Illustration" class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-2xl border border-white/20" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBXRqlRBnXPOUpmhBcGowWVCIMgnbmqS7eJ6MzFyQAuiIYe8AOYDMStUoukmUWCN8MRIfaIi1YOYZdd2_LhaAMOj5UqRR4dKJO86QYWJXRSTe1NV6wOZbSRPE9tnSqH6ykR0pqLMTT11U84pt_v_Bg5HQ1mMP0_2cWDTt6BftIERQpvTFtlzXT7o8gWOtQ0tXnDN-QGOEpC1sm80OeaMfYxW0Tu4blx94ljKHKIouQLTRxQ17RjDopYeYc1rKAHXocX_x9mJdUFhIeU"/>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Background accents -->
<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full pointer-events-none opacity-20">
<div class="absolute top-20 left-10 w-64 h-64 bg-primary-fixed rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-10 right-10 w-96 h-96 bg-on-primary-container rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Feature & Pricing Section -->
<section class="bg-surface-container-low py-section-padding-mobile md:py-section-padding-desktop px-gutter">
<div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
<!-- Pricing Card Column -->
<div class="lg:col-span-5">
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 md:p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-outline-variant flex flex-col gap-8 sticky top-32 transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
<div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg-mobile md:text-headline-lg text-primary">El poder del contenido auténtico</h2>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
                            En un mundo saturado de publicidad tradicional, las personas confían en personas. El contenido generado por el usuario (UGC) rompe la barrera de la desconfianza y conecta genuinamente con tu audiencia.
                        </p>
</div>
<div class="bg-surface-container p-6 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-between">
<div>
<span class="text-label-sm font-label-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant/60">Inversión desde</span>
<div class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-on-surface">$250 <span class="text-lg font-normal text-on-surface-variant">USD</span></div>
</div>
<span class="bg-primary-container/10 text-primary-container px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Plan Pro</span>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface">¿Qué incluye?</h3>
<ul class="flex flex-col gap-4">
<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">check_circle</span>
<span class="font-body-md">Diseño de script profesional</span>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">check_circle</span>
<span class="font-body-md">Selección de perfil especializado</span>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">check_circle</span>
<span class="font-body-md">1 video editado listo para publicar</span>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">check_circle</span>
<span class="font-body-md">Propuesta estratégica de contenido</span>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">check_circle</span>
<span class="font-body-md">1 Trafficker (30 días de optimización)</span>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<a href="/producto?service=creadores-ugc&plan=ugc" class="w-full bg-primary-container text-on-primary py-5 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:opacity-90 active:scale-95 transition-all shadow-md btn-magnetic press-effect text-center block">
                        <span class="icon-wrap">CONTRATAR AHORA</span>
                    </a>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Grid & Proof Column -->
<div class="lg:col-span-7 flex flex-col gap-8">
<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant">
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md mb-2">+3,500 creadores UGC listos</h3>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant">Consigue anuncios que sí venden y conecta con una red global de creadores apasionados por tu industria.</p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
<!-- Bento item 1 -->
<div class="md:col-span-2 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl group border border-outline-variant bg-white">
<img alt="Grid of UGC creator faces" class="w-full h-auto object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" data-alt="A diverse grid of smiling faces of people of different ethnicities and ages, looking directly into the camera as if participating in a video call. The mood is professional yet warm and friendly, emphasizing authentic human connection in a modern home-office setting. The lighting is soft and natural, maintaining the clean aesthetic of the brand with subtle purple tones in the background shadows." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBe2einU6nwpj_efl8NizXsNTJZBMcf67PrFXuljRvmianwgusmmt4Lj4beG6LPN3gDX2RRFXAw-xz5gOjkVBF5BctZ7AC-g-fxlGgXHurN7SyKix8MRIkDFaGWDI7JAzYxmU0_QZZnI2LxD2ktjuz2FnjRi6chTkELxNTRm80rqOughliPWAW5-0XKZDM2eNFOAGS_VCjaZ2AWwcDTadDp0UcHpXManZPkNZe3JL9IQkr4M9Jhqp4Rlv_Tcn4WzsVBU3i8xTWCJMcT"/>
</div>
<div class="bg-primary-container p-8 rounded-2xl text-on-primary flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[240px]">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl" data-icon="trending_up">trending_up</span>
<div>
<div class="text-4xl font-bold mb-1">94%</div>
<p class="font-body-md text-on-primary-container">Mayor confianza del consumidor comparado con anuncios tradicionales.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="bg-surface-container-highest p-8 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[240px]">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary" data-icon="rocket_launch">rocket_launch</span>
<div>
<div class="text-4xl font-bold mb-1">X3</div>
<p class="font-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Incremento promedio en CTR en campañas de Meta Ads y TikTok.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Simple Portfolio Section Placeholder -->
<section class="py-section-padding-mobile md:py-section-padding-desktop px-gutter max-w-container-max mx-auto">
<div class="text-center mb-16">
<span class="text-primary font-label-sm uppercase tracking-widest">Portafolio</span>
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg-mobile md:text-headline-lg mt-4">Nuestras Historias de Éxito</h2>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
<div class="aspect-[9/16] bg-surface-container rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-outline-variant group">
<div class="w-full h-full bg-cover bg-center" data-alt="Vertical mobile video frame showing a young woman unboxing a premium skincare set with a delighted expression. The scene is bright and airy with high-end minimalist decor in the background. The lighting is flattering and highlights the product textures clearly. Purple atmospheric accents tie back to the brand identity." style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDboCNNlPWryZ8dsbTiECWgkBWHImZk9tG1Cax08w_IXqJPOPic5Zl3zHizfjaPMltgLV2ELYlg5ZyzgRVohg_uQ1djFTkqnamRncsuLdpjwGVE8uuqdFGWbdGsJWP9HkUm0KBW3F33ohp-iWePSYzHyNlzS2eW5lKz546OVP9NjwtSY_uj3WceI_WmI_Pb0rZVfmiNLKAqpDPuO6At_x92z5wnpyMHtw_zpGV2plOBthD98sjOsJbWGvmgu-QV-myHYtpfU2CUhcWG')">
<div class="w-full h-full bg-black/20 group-hover:bg-black/40 transition-all flex items-center justify-center">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-6xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transform scale-50 group-hover:scale-100 transition-all" data-icon="play_circle">play_circle</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="aspect-[9/16] bg-surface-container rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-outline-variant group">
<div class="w-full h-full bg-cover bg-center" data-alt="A group of diverse friends laughing and looking at a smartphone together in a modern city loft. The vibe is genuine, candid, and full of energy. The overall aesthetic is clean and high-contrast, fitting a modern digital agency style with warm ambient lighting." style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCiIhPHIZBKTe0uvdORmL_uq_PQwTRd82VEzNYCaDWA6Q_9AxBvEu-Us_iSjkhp6DuelcfbN97lzCKb6tbeXQDX82XQexvUyoOt4wTRF27HPm38P2RxODOT_IiwiLONephr8Vr1kvf7Jsv07kzcL7Dj6zF1m4NwYpxYfyCpEQX4DfsFz_GB5Ou19ItY3oFyi0IWgShR9HAPljrGZbj-wcjNpzwOddc_Rm0CcJN6aHpBvMETQjX7A2I4c_KMNXFi8FhDkIWwRAw8wqKI')">
<div class="w-full h-full bg-black/20 group-hover:bg-black/40 transition-all flex items-center justify-center">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-6xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transform scale-50 group-hover:scale-100 transition-all" data-icon="play_circle">play_circle</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="aspect-[9/16] bg-surface-container rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-outline-variant group">
<div class="w-full h-full bg-cover bg-center" data-alt="Close up of a creator speaking passionately into a high-quality desktop microphone while gestures with their hands. Authentic domestic setting with soft depth of field. High-end digital creator aesthetic with crisp focus and professional color grading featuring deep purples and clean whites." style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuD8qSJsGNPoruK-E2kLSOU-y5ltd-OSSuZzvaiYXv68ZC6z4qkjKa8n8AZh8sG8JkFsLG0t5vNjjrYfJV5FcOh8VBrioinH5NT6vwI6mqY0WbFYkvRaClB67rJV9BRxK-wvEzepuAwtP-A85LQC0sCOfQFDEWfwKIdoRR4v7G9R8cZt6O9K4WU0e_Cw42gutiTDfN8geD7JoUxoqKmAcW7aN5Q7HGEJi1jUqXtpU31INLZz_MmvxiQAaN6ny6AMFoeruYLSSJ5vTrSg')">
<div class="w-full h-full bg-black/20 group-hover:bg-black/40 transition-all flex items-center justify-center">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-6xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transform scale-50 group-hover:scale-100 transition-all" data-icon="play_circle">play_circle</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</Layout>
